Motormaster/ Wildrider/Speedbreaker

He first looks to the council, "Yeah, we will want to" he returns to the
comm-link, "Who is this?" Motormaster demands, then after he hears the
response, he at first puts his hand to his head, feeling theyve got a
jester as a member. But as he hears that Cyclonus and Scourge are there, he
smiles. "Good, good, welcome to the Decepticons, Cyclonus, I have a
speacial task for you."


Inside the Dark Avian

Wildrider turns to see Drag Strip arrive, "well you lost the race rust for
brains" a smile crossing his face as he says it.
